	<entry name="uwu_SemtexianBombardiers_BombastFieldGun" value="Noble Mk XVI Field Howitzer"/>
	<entry name="uwu_SemtexianBombardiers_BombastFieldGunFlavor" value="Artillery guns fire with great force, throwing the weapon back. Most platforms include recoil-dampening measures, but Noble pattern howitzers are known to be especially stable, making them effective but relatively rare. Its other strength lies in its versatility; the firing arc can be adjusted to allow for indirect or direct fire."/>
